---
import MarketingLayout from '@/layouts/MarketingLayout.astro'
import Section from '@/components/marketing/Section.astro'
---

<MarketingLayout
  title="Security"
  description="Learn about Quatro's security practices and compliance certifications."
>
  <Section>
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl">
      <h1 class="font-display text-3xl font-bold text-neutral-800 sm:text-4xl">Security</h1>
      <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-neutral-500">Last updated: February 2026</p>

      <div class="prose prose-neutral mt-8">
        <p class="text-neutral-600">
          Security is fundamental to everything we do at Quatro. Our platform is built on a zero-trust architecture designed to meet the security requirements of critical infrastructure operators.
        </p>

        <h2 class="mt-8 font-display text-xl font-bold text-neutral-800">Security Features</h2>
        <ul class="mt-4 space-y-2 text-neutral-600">
          <li>End-to-end encryption</li>
          <li>Role-based access control</li>
          <li>Audit logging</li>
          <li>SOC 2 Type II certified</li>
          <li>ISO 27001 certified</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="mt-8 font-display text-xl font-bold text-neutral-800">Responsible Disclosure</h2>
        <p class="mt-4 text-neutral-600">
          If you discover a security vulnerability, please report it to security@quatro.io.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </Section>
</MarketingLayout>
